{
  "stem": "294.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we still had a pretty nice wedding-- and with the only rabbi that was left in the city-- a very orthodox rabbi, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for the first time in my life, I saw, you know, the young couple staying under the chuppah, and the-- no-- the-- the bride has to go around her-- the groom seven times, or whatever, you know?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was-- well, this was exactly the first wedding I attended, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was still young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- and then you started to-- you-- you tried to study in Krakow?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews could not-- were not accepted in universities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my-- my husband could not teach, because the Jewish schools were closed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was not allowed to teach in the Polish schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were supposed to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working-- both of us, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that particular time, we were working for the Jewish Federation in the office, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also what the Germans loved to do-- catch the people on the street to shovel snow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They thought this is something very important, you know, that we had to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But mostly men did it, at the very beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't bother the woman that much yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother was with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, in-- what was it-- November-- I think of September, maybe, of 1940, there was a new decree.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whoever came after September 1, 1939, to the city of Krakow has to leave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we tried everything to use the connections that we had, possibly to allow my mother to stay.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
